title: A/B
description:
Statement

Given two integers A and B, calculate A/B.
input:
Input

On the first line, two integers A and B are given. (0 < A, B < 10)
output:
Output

Print a single real number A/B.

The answer will be considered correct if the absolute or relative error doesn't exceed 10-9.
sample_explain_1: You don't have to print exactly nine decimal digits.
